dc_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for Hackensack River, N.J. in 3 sheets, sheet 1, from Saw Mill Creek to Paterson Plank Road Bridge at Secaucus
dc_description_s: Map showing the pierhead and bulkhead lines of various business and private properties along the Hackensack River, from Saw Mill Creek to Paterson Plank Road Bridge at Secaucus. Also summarizes location of monuments with survey sketches.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|File No. 5/35 Hack. Riv.|Drawn by P.B.
